com.guardtime.ksi.unisignature.verifier

Interface VerificationContext


  • public interface VerificationContext
    This interface represents a verification context. Verification context contains information needed for verification.

                                        throws KSIException
        Returns extended signature calendar hash chain
        Parameters:
        publicationTime - publication time to extend
        Returns:
        instance of extended signature calendar hash chain
        Throws:
        KSIException - when extending fails

      • getExtendedCalendarHashChain

        CalendarHashChain getExtendedCalendarHashChain()
                                        throws KSIException
        Returns extended calendar hash chain. The signature is extended to a top of the calendar.
        Returns:
        instance of extended calendar hash chain
        Throws:
        KSIException - when extending fails.

      • getUserProvidedPublication

        PublicationData getUserProvidedPublication()
        Returns user provided publication. If user has not provided the publication then this method returns null.

      • getDocumentHash

        DataHash getDocumentHash()
        Returns the document hash provided by the user or calculated from the input data. Returns null when document is missing.

      • getInputHashLevel

        Long getInputHashLevel()
        Returns the input hash level provided by the user. Returns null if not provided.

      • isExtendingAllowed

        boolean isExtendingAllowed()
        True when extending is allowed when using UserProvidedPublicationBasedVerificationPolicy or PublicationsFileBasedVerificationPolicy
